fields.title: Excel Essentials
fields.description: Learn to perform the top 20% of essential Excel skills that you can put to use every-day and apply them to real-word scenarios.  Build well-designed 'flexible' worksheets that do the hard work for you.  Analyze results with formulas, filters and conditional formatting.  Increase your speed with hotkeys and other efficient techniques.

fields.title: Excel Lookups
fields.description: Learn to create lookup formulas and apply them to real-world scenarios.  Handle errors and return default values.  Perform double-lookups on tables with 2 matching criteria.  Write a lookup formula that retrieves a value to the left.

fields.title: Excel Pivot Tables
fields.description: Learn the advantages of using Pivot Tables in your everyday work.  Create pivot tables, pivot your data into the desired view and slice-and-dice it to get the answers you need.  Make your pivot tables interactive and visual with slicers and conditional formatting.  Understand how to build calculated fields.
